हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: After 8 years in a coma, a hidden billionaire returns to win back his love and take revenge on those who thought he was just an intern. He came to live among the common man to find true love… but before he could tell Suhana the truth, a freak accident left him unconscious.
